column5: do we have to cheer for the sens?  They are good enough, nasty enough, fast enough and strong enough.  I have/had a number of signed leafs stuff, they are my boys...but how good are these guys in black and red?
It may come to pass. I sat next to a Ottawa season ticket holder at a Leaf-Sabre game who was a true believer that actually argued a strong case for it.

I'm a real leaf fan at heart as well. But! I do think that the Sens have the team to do it and I hope they go all the way. I actually work for Mr. Melnyk and he really deserves the Stanley Cup. He's been able to keep the team very competitive and he's a great guy too boot! I sometimes think Toronto fans are upset to see that Ottawa can continue to do so well and wish that our leafs could be more like them.
Emery has been fantastic. Great overall team effort. Go Sens...Canada's best chance I think.
I'm a diehard wings fan but I'm thinkin Buffalo/Vancouver for the final series
My Sabres are sputterin too much to go past second round. Thats my opinion
Out of habit I'm still going to hope for Sens being eliminated.  The only reason they have for hope is they didn't have to face the Leafs.
Great talent , lots of depth and a fast team, very entertaining and I believe they have the heart now.  Sens all the way  Matt the sens fan
Dang and Double Dang.  It was a god run for a bunch of preadolescent teens
